{"tid":1594520,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"* 如果有一天 可以回到從前","createTime":"2019-09-25T15:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:38:52.000Z","uid":102397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b55dd054a09d82f354c6f5b876b1c3f791a39a","tid":1594520,"uid":102397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"如果返到去之前你話幾好 可惜有好多野都吾同左<br />\n就算你有幾中意果個人 但果個人都吾再在意你<br />\n就算有幾吾捨得都好 只可以同自己講吾好再咁犯賤<br />\n因為果個人同你一齊既時候個心都只係係個前度到<br />\n雖然一齊過都有一段時間但根本最愛既都吾係自己<br />\n明明分左手兩年幾 點解仲會成日諗起佢<br />\n去到一齊去過既地方又諗起佢 諗返起一齊經歷過既野<br />\n之後果種感覺真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打絲打好似我咁⋯"},{"pid":"fc8af2731bb75e1f618c731aff2e82e0db4e0035","tid":1594520,"uid":50161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"19c823968bec06766ff33ecf8a6ba8ed98354aa7","tid":1594520,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"分左手兩年幾都放唔低，你咁樣好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c19c1000750915c5cd6e894d80cd7b142dd49","tid":1594520,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:32:27.000Z","msg":"唱左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde424882ea00d885da83d2e408a82d74e72bc52","tid":1594520,"uid":102397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c823968bec06766ff33ecf8a6ba8ed98354aa7","tid":1594520,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"分左手兩年幾都放唔低，你咁樣好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"係⋯點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70129df7c2fa2a865e9fa698bd15dc16ab449e81","tid":1594520,"uid":102397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877c19c1000750915c5cd6e894d80cd7b142dd49","tid":1594520,"uid":24737